# Government Tender Announcement

## Contract Information
### Tender Title
* English: Computerized Mat Cutter W0133-23T001
* French: Découpeuse de passe-partout informatique W0133-23T001

### Tender Reference Number
* Reference Number: WS3530634820
* Solicitation Number: WS3530634820
* Amendment Number: 1

### Public Tender Notice Information
* Publication Date: [September 7, 2022](https://www.google.com/search?q=date%3A2022-09-07)
* Tender Closing Date: [October 19, 2022](https://www.google.com/search?q=date%3A2022-10-19)
* Amendment Date: [October 13, 2022](https://www.google.com/search?q=date%3A2022-10-18)

### Contract Details
* Procurement Category: *Goods and Services (GD)
* Contract Category: [Request for Proposal](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Request_for_proposal)
* Tendering Method: *Competitive - Open bidding
* Selection Criteria: Lowest Price

### Trade Agreements
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

### Contract Location
* Regions of Operation: *British Columbia, Canada
* Contracting Entity: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
* Contracting Entity Address: 
  * 11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage
  * Gatineau, Quebec, K1A 0S5, Canada

### Contract Description
The Government of Canada has a requirement for one (1) Computerized Mat Cutter (CMC) Machine and table to be delivered to the Department of National Defence. This contract includes onsite delivery, installation, software, training, and ongoing support.

### Contact Information
* Contact Name: Patrick Wass
* Contact Email: patrick.wass@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca

For further information and to obtain the full tender notice, please refer to the official Government of Canada tender website: [http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14042276?extsite=MTQwNDIyNzZfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14042276?extsite=MTQwNDIyNzZfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk
